  "title": "3-6 months Dental Assistant (Entry Level) #HJO",
  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Chairside assisting in operative dentistry, surgical procedures</li>\n  <li>Adhere to infection control and work safety regulations</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and monitor temperature of dental fridge and materials</li>\n  <li>Ensure tidiness of consultation rooms</li>\n  <li>Perform other ad hoc duties as instructed by the supervisor</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min. N / O / A Level / NITEC / Diploma in any field</li>\n  <li>Comfortable with hands-on, clinical support duties</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates are invited to email your resume to:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>jen.ooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Jenalyn Ooi Huai Sian (R1765551)</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>\n<p><br></p>",
